## Option B — 6mzhe1-yf Admin API (theme, products, locales)

Live store operations use gitignored `.env` and repo scripts — not the docs-only MCP.

- Store: `6mzhe1-yf.myshopify.com` (primary domain **`https://mitipi.eu`**; `www.mitipi.eu` redirects to apex; `mitipi-2.myshopify.com` is a connected alias only).
- Token: `SHOPIFY_CLIENT_ID` + `SHOPIFY_CLIENT_SECRET` → `./scripts/shopify-refresh-admin-token.sh`, or auto-refresh in `scripts/lib/shopify-admin-gql.mjs`.
- Product mutations need lurafi app scope `write_products` (see `docs/FIX-LURAFI-APP-AND-PRODUCTS.md`).
- Theme push: `npm run shopify:publish:mitipi` / Shopify CLI with `SHOPIFY_FLAG_STORE=6mzhe1-yf.myshopify.com`.

